## 🔧 Installation

### Option 1: WSL2 (Windows 10/11)
```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install bwa samtools freebayes snpeff fastqc trimmomatic bcftools -y
pip install -r requirements.txt
python3 app.py
# Open http://127.0.0.1:5002
```

Option 2: Docker

```bash
docker-compose up -d
# Open http://localhost:5002
```

